===Noun===
'''charcoal'''
#impure [[carbon]] obtained by heating [[wood]] or other organic matter in the absence of [[oxygen]].
#a stick of black carbon material used for drawing.
#a drawing made with charcoal. 
#(''colour'') a very dark [[gray]] [[colour]].
